    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 represents a superlative example of the high-revving S65 platform. The 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 delivers linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline, paired with a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox. Chassis integrity is absolute, featuring Electronic Damping Control (EDC) and a pristine subframe. This vehicle boasts original paint depth and a documented service history, ensuring the variable M differential and rod bearings remain in peak operating specification. A concourse-grade specimen for the discerning collector.",
