    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom condition since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with zero swirls, chips, or imperfections. Every body panel is perfectly aligned, and the alloy wheels are completely free of curb rash, wrapped in premium tires with near-full tread. Step inside to find an interior that still smells like the factory floor; the hand-stitched leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, and the dashboard is pristine with no sun fading or scratches on the trim. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been strictly maintained at authorized dealerships, with a complete folder of service records available for inspection. The engine idles silently, shifts are imperceptibly smooth, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean. All electronics, from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control, function exactly as they did the day it was delivered. This is not just a used car; it is a meticulously curated piece of automotive excellence ready for its next discerning owner.",
